Ford Motor Company Reaffirms FY 2012 Operating Profit Guidance; Comments On H2 2012 Operating Profit Guidance
Friday, 27 Apr 2012 07:01am EDT
Ford Motor Company announced that it continues to expect solid results for fiscal 2012, with total company pre-tax operating profits about equal to fiscal 2011. The Company expects pre-tax operating profit in the second half of 2012 to be slightly higher than the first half of 2012 due to the cadence of its many product launches and capacity actions.Â 
